categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A member of the Jedi Order, this Human served in the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. After surviving Order 66, he did battle with Dark Jedi Namman Cha, pitting the power of Faalo's Will against his opponent.
This Jedi was created for the Wizards of the Coast Star Wars Roleplaying Game. Unnamed, he was placed on a card demonstrating Faalo's Will.
